{"tid":1136843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海關機場檢未完稅加熱煙市值14萬　兩男落網","createTime":"2019-05-03T09:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T10:03:34.000Z","uid":241764,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"124b6401f15c9dddac62393e8f386263c63ce245","tid":1136843,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"兩名50歲男旅客昨晚(2日)從日本大阪飛抵香港，海關人員替他們清關，在他們的隨身行李內發現約4.8萬支懷疑未完稅加熱非燃燒煙草產品，以及約250粒懷疑未完稅加熱非燃燒煙草膠囊，故拘捕該兩男子。<br />\n<br />\n海關指，上述製品估計市值共約14萬港元，應課稅值約9萬港元，案件仍在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190503/photo/bkn-20190503170345237-0503_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190503171755\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190503%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190503170345237-0503_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190503171755&h=c6458f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190503/bkn-20190503170345237-0503_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190503%2Fbkn-20190503170345237-0503_00822_001.html&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=7ff1123b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190503/bkn-20190503170345237-0503_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"16755437117b77554b3f765fc12f030d01412ddb","tid":1136843,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"1f4d5fb86203a0d0b46b5c979fa2ccbd9b7b1a1f","tid":1136843,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T10:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐監啦死廢老"}]}